---
// Google Reviews - Social Proof
---

<section class="py-6" style="background: #FAFAFA;">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="reviews-header text-center mb-5">
      <div class="rating-badge mb-3">
        <span class="stars">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</span>
        <span class="rating-text">4.8/5</span>
        <span class="review-count">(127 reseñas)</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="display-6 fw-bold">Lo que dicen nuestros clientes</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="row g-4">
      <!-- Review 1 -->
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <div class="review-card p-4">
          <div class="review-stars mb-2">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</div>
          <p class="review-text">"Cambio de batería en 2h. Técnico muy profesional. Volvería sin dudarlo."</p>
          <div class="review-author">
            <span class="author-name">Juan P.</span>
            <span class="author-device">(iPhone 12)</span>
            <span class="review-date">• Enero 2026</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Review 2 -->
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <div class="review-card p-4">
          <div class="review-stars mb-2">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</div>
          <p class="review-text">"Repararon mi MacBook M1. Muy rápido y con garantía. Excelente."</p>
          <div class="review-author">
            <span class="author-name">María G.</span>
            <span class="author-device">(MacBook)</span>
            <span class="review-date">• Enero 2026</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Review 3 -->
      <div class="col-lg-4">
        <div class="review-card p-4">
          <div class="review-stars mb-2">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</div>
          <p class="review-text">"Diagnóstico gratis y presupuesto claro. Sin sorpresas. Muy recomendado."</p>
          <div class="review-author">
            <span class="author-name">Carlos R.</span>
            <span class="author-device">(iPad Pro)</span>
            <span class="review-date">• Diciembre 2025</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-5">
      <a href="https://www.google.com/search?q=pipod+bogota" target="_blank" class="btn-reviews">Ver todas las reseñas en Google</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .rating-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #fff;
    padding: 16px 32px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  }

  .stars {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-right: 8px;
  }

  .rating-text {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    color: #000;
    margin-right: 8px;
  }

  .review-count {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #666;
  }

  .review-card {
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 20px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .review-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
  }

  .review-stars {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #FFB800;
  }

  .review-text {
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #333;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    min-height: 80px;
  }

  .review-author {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #888;
  }

  .author-name {
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #000;
  }

  .author-device {
    color: #3A506B;
  }

  .review-date {
    color: #999;
  }

  .btn-reviews {
    background: #fff;
    color: #3A506B;
    border: 2px solid #3A506B;
    padding: 14px 32px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    display: inline-block;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .btn-reviews:hover {
    background: #3A506B;
    color: #fff;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(58, 80, 107, 0.3);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .review-card {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .rating-text {
      font-size: 1.2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
